84 Lumber Super Bowl Commercial 2017 - The Entire Journey 
84 Lumber is making a big statement in their 2017 Super Bowl Commercial ! 
The lumber company’s commercial follows the touching story of a mother and her young daughter as they make the trek from Mexico to the United States. 
Defeating all odds, the mother-daughter duo make it the border, only to be met with a giant wall that stretches on for miles. 
The family looks completely defeated, until they realize just feet away is a giant door welcoming them to the US – made from 84 lumber. 
“The will to succeed is always welcome here,” the screen reads at the end of the commercial.
